OL,6,FThe father of a man from Kent who was
OL,7,Fcrushed to death says the pain of
OL,8,Flosing him has been unbearable.
OL,10,FLiam McArdle, from Gravesend, was
OL,11,Ffatally crushed by an excavator
OL,12,Fattachment while working for Erith
OL,13,FPlant Services Limited on 21 September
OL,14,F2021.
OL,16,FA demolition grab, attached to an
OL,17,Fexcavator, fell onto the 24-year-old
OL,18,Fwhile it was loaded onto a lorry at
OL,19,FErith Plant Services Limited's
OL,20,Fworkshop at Eastern Quarry on Watling
OL,21,FSteet, Swanscombe.
