OL,6,FLiam's dad says the pain since losing
OL,7,Fhis son has been unbearable.
OL,9,FDeclan McArdle said in his victim
OL,10,Fpersonal statement: "The pain of
OL,11,Flosing my son has been and will
OL,12,Fcontinue to be unbearable.
OL,14,F"Liam worked hard and wanted to learn.
OL,15,FHe wanted to follow in my footsteps,
OL,16,Fand I was proud of the person he was
OL,17,Fbecoming.
