OL,3,CFather of man who was crushed to death
OL,4,Csays pain of losing him is unbearable
OL,6,F"Liam and I enjoyed spending time
OL,7,Ftogether. We would go on truck rallies
OL,8,Fand to car racing events together.
OL,9,FLiam would never really say: 'I love
OL,10,Fyou, dad.' It just wasn't his way.
OL,12,F"Rather, he would ask me to go to a
OL,13,Fracing event with him and I knew that
OL,14,Fthis was Liam's way of saying he loved
OL,15,Fme.
OL,17,F"Liam and I were planning on going to
OL,18,Fa racing event in February 2022. I
OL,19,Fwent to the event, and I took Liam's
OL,20,Fashes with me so that we could still
OL,21,Fgo together."
