OL,6,FA Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,7,Finvestigation found Erith Plant
OL,8,FServices Limited failed to ensure
OL,9,Fthere was a safe method of work while
OL,10,Floading and unloading excavators and
OL,11,Fattachments.
OL,13,FThere was also no defined segregation
OL,14,Fbetween vehicles and pedestrians at
OL,15,Fthe firm's Eastern Quarry workshop,
OL,16,Fnor was there suitable supervision of
OL,17,Fwork activities.
